---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="What Is a Data Center? The Engine of the Modern World"
    description="Learn how data centers power everyday life, from healthcare to AI, and why they are the essential infrastructure of the 21st century."
>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 border-b border-tech-blue/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-pine-green/80 to-tech-blue/80 z-0 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558494949-ef010cbdcc31?q=80&w=2668&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center z-0 opacity-40 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">What Is a Data Center? <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-teal-300 block mt-3">The Engine of the Modern World</span></h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-200 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed font-light">
                Demystifying the incredible facilities that act as the true backbone of our modern, interconnected lives.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            
            <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none mb-16">
                <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-10 text-slate-700 font-medium">
                    A data center is the physical facility that stores, processes, and transmits the data that powers the modern world. It is the home of the cloud, the backbone of the internet, and the engine of artificial intelligence. Every time you stream a movie, attend a telehealth appointment, check the weather, use GPS navigation, send an email, or work remotely, you are relying on a data center to process and deliver that information to you in milliseconds.
                </p>

                <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                    Inside a data center are thousands of specialized computers called servers, alongside the networking equipment, cooling systems, and power infrastructure required to keep them running continuously, 24 hours a day, 365 days a year. Because our modern lives depend on these systems, data centers are built to be extraordinarily reliable. They often achieve what the industry calls "five nines" uptime, meaning they are operational <strong class="text-slate-900 font-bold bg-tech-blue/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">99.999% of the time</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Infographic Placeholder Section -->
            <div class="my-20 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-8 lg:p-16 shadow-lg text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-tech-blue/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-pine-green/5 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white shadow-md rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 text-tech-blue ring-1 ring-slate-100">
                        <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">The Invisible Flow of Innovation</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
                        Data travels continuously from your device, across vast fiber optic networks, directly into the servers housed in secure data centers, and back again in a fraction of a second.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-6 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6">
                        <!-- Workflow visualization -->
                        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 w-full flex-1">
                            <span class="block text-5xl mb-4">📱</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Your Devices</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Streaming, Banking, Medical</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="text-tech-blue/40 flex flex-col items-center">
                            <svg class="w-10 h-10 hidden md:block" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                               <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                            </svg>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase my-2 text-slate-400">Milliseconds</span>
                            <svg class="w-10 h-10 hidden md:block" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                               <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18" />
                            </svg>
                            
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 md:hidden my-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-blue to-blue-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-transparent w-full flex-1 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-2xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
                            <span class="block text-5xl mb-4 relative z-10">🏢</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-lg relative z-10">Secure Data Center</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-blue-200 mt-2 relative z-10">Instant Processing & Storage</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 tracking-tight">The Infrastructure of the 21st Century</h2>
                <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6 text-slate-600">
                    Throughout history, new infrastructure has consistently unlocked new eras of prosperity. Data centers are the essential infrastructure of the 21st century in the exact same way that railroads were the essential infrastructure of the 19th century, and the interstate highway system was the essential infrastructure of the 20th century. 
                </p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed mb-8 text-slate-600">
                    Just as those historic investments transformed rural economies and connected communities to national prosperity, data centers are doing the same today, ensuring that the technology of tomorrow is rooted right here in our communities.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What is an AI Data Center (Breakout Section) -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-slate-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Abstract background -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-blue/20 to-purple-900/40 z-0"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-tech-blue/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
        
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
                <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-tech-blue/20 text-blue-200 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-6 border border-tech-blue/30 backdrop-blur-sm">The Next Evolution</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">What is an AI Data Center?</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
                    An AI data center is a specialized facility packed with thousands of high-performance accelerators (GPUs, TPUs, or custom AI chips) that run the massive parallel computations required for modern artificial intelligence. Unlike traditional data centers that mostly store websites, emails, or videos, an AI data center is purpose-built for training and running giant AI models—the "brains" behind tools like Grok, ChatGPT, image generators, and recommendation engines.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-tech-blue-light mt-8">Think of it as a super-computer factory dedicated entirely to intelligence at scale.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- What does it actually do? Cards -->
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-24">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-10 text-white">What does it actually do?</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <!-- Training -->
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm group">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-tech-blue/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-blue-300 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                            <span class="text-2xl">🧠</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Training</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">It feeds enormous datasets into neural networks so they can learn patterns (e.g. teaching a model to understand language, recognize images, or predict protein structures).</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Inference -->
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm group">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-pine-green/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-green-300 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                            <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Inference</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">It runs the trained models in real time to answer your questions, generate images, translate languages, drive recommendation systems, or power autonomous features.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Research -->
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm group">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-amber-300 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                            <span class="text-2xl">🔬</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Research & Scaling</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Scientists and engineers use it to experiment with new AI architectures, fine-tune models, and dramatically push the frontier of what's technologically possible.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-10">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Why is it important?</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        AI data centers are the engine of the current technological revolution. Without them:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-tech-blue-light mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                            <span class="text-slate-300">Large language models and generative AI simply could not exist at today's level.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-tech-blue-light mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                            <span class="text-slate-300">Progress in medicine, climate science, materials discovery, and autonomous systems would slow dramatically.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-tech-blue-light mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                            <span class="text-slate-300">Companies and researchers would be limited to small-scale experiments instead of world-changing breakthroughs.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="bg-tech-blue/20 border-l-4 border-tech-blue p-6 rounded-r-xl">
                        <p class="text-white font-medium">
                            They are now considered critical national infrastructure in many countries because AI is expected to add <strong class="text-tech-blue-light">$15–20 trillion to global GDP by 2030</strong> (comparable to the entire current U.S. economy). In short, they turn electricity and silicon into intelligence, and intelligence is the ultimate multiplier of human progress.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">How does it make the internet better?</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        AI data centers are why the internet feels dramatically smarter and more useful today than it did even five years ago:
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start">
                             <span class="text-2xl mr-4">🤖</span>
                             <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Instant, Context-Aware Answers</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Instead of ten blue links (think Grok or Perplexity).</p>
                             </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start">
                             <span class="text-2xl mr-4">🎯</span>
                             <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Hyper-Personalized Experiences</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Netflix knows what you want, Amazon recommends the right tool, Google Maps routes based on live AI predictions.</p>
                             </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start">
                             <span class="text-2xl mr-4">✍️</span>
                             <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Generative Capabilities</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Create images, write code, summarize documents, or get real-time translations directly in your browser.</p>
                             </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start">
                             <span class="text-2xl mr-4">🔍</span>
                             <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Smarter Search & Discovery</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">AI understands user intent and complex nuance, not just exact keywords.</p>
                             </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-200 mt-6 italic">The result: the internet is evolving from a giant library of static pages into a dynamic, intelligent assistant.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Specific Benefits Grid -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-slate-50 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6">Direct Benefits to Humans</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Here's what actual compute power translates to in everyday life. Hover over the tiles to explore the real-world impact.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-tech-blue/50 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-default relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-tech-blue/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-tech-blue group-hover:bg-tech-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Productivity</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">AI assistants draft emails, code, reports, and presentations, saving human workers hours every single week.</p>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-tech-blue to-blue-400 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-pine-green/50 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-default relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pine-green/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-pine-green group-hover:bg-pine-green group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Healthcare</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Faster drug discovery, groundbreaking AI diagnostics that catch diseases earlier, and hyper-personalized medicine.</p>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-pine-green to-emerald-400 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-amber-500/50 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-default relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-amber-500 group-hover:bg-amber-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Education</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Highly personalized tutors that instantly adapt to an individual's learning style, available 24/7 for free or low cost.</p>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-yellow-400 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-default relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-purple-500 group-hover:bg-purple-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Accessibility</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Real-time instant translation across global languages, voice-to-text for the deaf, and dynamic image descriptions for the blind.</p>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-fuchsia-400 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-default relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-500/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-pink-500 group-hover:bg-pink-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Entertainment</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Flawless content curation and recommendations, personalized AI-generated art, music, gaming assets, and immersive experiences.</p>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-rose-400 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all duration-300 group cursor-default relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Science & Environment</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Accelerated hyper-accurate climate modeling, the rapid discovery of new battery materials, and algorithmic efficiency in energy grids.</p>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-400 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Conclusion Bar -->
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-tech-blue/5 border border-tech-blue/20 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">The Bottom Line</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium">
                    AI data centers are the hidden infrastructure that turns raw computing power into tools that amplify human creativity, solve hard problems, and make life noticeably easier and more interesting. They're not just "tech stuff in a warehouse" — they're the reason the internet went from helpful to genuinely intelligent, and why the next decade of innovation is going to feel like science fiction becoming everyday reality.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">
                    *Closed-loop designs help keep their environmental footprint minimal while delivering these massive gains.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Next CTA from previously -->
            <div class="mt-24 pt-10 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-center">
